IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: JERI-HILL PROVIDES AFFORDABLE HOUSING TO THE ELDERLY WHO ARE INCOME ELIGIBLE. MANAGEMENT PROVIDES SERVICES CONSISTING OF DEVELOPMENT, MANAGEMENT, AND MAINTENANCE OF HOUSING PROJECTS ALONG WITH OTHER SPECIAL ASSISTANCE DESIGNED TO IMPROVE THE QUALITY OF LIFE OF THE RESIDENTS OF THE HOUSING PROJECTS INCLUDING WELLNESS NURSING.
